Nigeria’s Global Fleet Group Opens Bank in Ghana, GNA Says

-- B y   J a s o n   M c L u r e
-- 
2011-02-23T10:38:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-23/nigeria-s-global-fleet-group-opens-bank-in-ghana-gna-says.html
  Nigeria ’s  Global Fleet Group  has
opened a bank in Ghana, one of five lenders Nigerian businessman
Jimoh Ibrahim plans to open by 2013, the  Ghana  News Agency
reported, citing Ibrahim.  Energy Bank Ghana Ltd., the 27th bank to be registered in
the West African nation, was opened with a shareholders’ fund of
60 million cedis ($39.8 million), the state-run news agency
cited Ibrahim as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jason McLure in Accra on 
 jmclure@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at  barden@bloomberg.net  